item.title: Im so confused
item.dc:creator: @ethanhello ethanhello
item.description:
@ethanhello wrote:

Click the link and download both the version 7 for JRE and JDK

http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html

Then change your run.bat to this

@echo off Title Client cd ./ "C:\Program Files\Java\jre7\bin\java.exe" -Xmx500m Gui 30 0 lowmem members 32 pause

Then tell me how it goes, that should fix it
